    <item>
      <title>中国最大券商在股市暴跌后限制卖空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/china-s-biggest-brokerage-restricts-short-sales-after-stock-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于中国股市进一步暴跌，中国最大的券商已暂停对内地市场部分客户的卖空。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/china-s-biggest-brokerage-restricts-short-sales-after-stock-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:56:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着股市下跌，中国共同基金以五年来最快速度崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/china-mutual-fund-liquidations-hit-five-year-high-as-stocks-sink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市的暴跌正在对该国的资产管理行业造成严重破坏，将共同基金关闭数量推至五年来新高，这是投资者信心减弱的另一个迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/china-mutual-fund-liquidations-hit-five-year-high-as-stocks-sink</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:43:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>盛宝表示判断中国股市何时触底还为时过早</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-19/saxo-say-too-early-to-tell-when-china-market-will-bottom-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首席中国策略师黄雷蒙 (Redmond Wong) 讨论了世界第二大经济体的前景、政府政策和股市。中国股市基准周四下午交易中反弹，一些主要交易所交易基金的成交量大幅上升，引发人们猜测，国家基金的买入可能是这一逆转背后的原因。黄在“彭博市场：中国公开赛”上发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-19/saxo-say-too-early-to-tell-when-china-market-will-bottom-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:10:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市周四突然上涨表明国家基金买入ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-19/china-s-sudden-rally-points-to-state-funds-etf-buying-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市基准周四下午交易中反弹。一些主要交易所交易基金成交量的大幅上升引发了人们的猜测，即国家基金的买入可能是这一逆转背后的原因。涂莲婷、冼丽贝卡在彭博电视上解释。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-19/china-s-sudden-rally-points-to-state-funds-etf-buying-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 01:43:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率上升威胁印度信贷增长并压低利润率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/rising-interest-rates-threaten-india-s-credit-growth-and-pressure-margins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度顶级私营部门贷款机构的收益可能表明，随着利率周期见顶，由利率上升推动的信贷增长强劲和利润率上升目前面临着放缓的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/rising-interest-rates-threaten-india-s-credit-growth-and-pressure-margins</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 01:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Whitehaven 考虑将 20% 的煤矿出售给钢铁生产商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/whitehaven-studies-sale-of-20-of-key-mine-to-steel-producers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Whitehaven Coal Ltd. 正在研究向全球钢铁制造商出售 Blackwater 煤矿 20% 股份的方案，并努力敲定价值 32 亿美元的两项澳大利亚资产交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/whitehaven-studies-sale-of-20-of-key-mine-to-steel-producers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 23:30:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券的巨大转变让交易者密切关注美国国债收益率的一举一动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/when-will-the-treasury-yield-curve-return-to-normal-and-steepen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员越来越相信，美国国债收益率即将恢复到其存在以来大部分时间的交易方式——使金融市场保持活力的是正常化的方式、原因和时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/when-will-the-treasury-yield-curve-return-to-normal-and-steepen</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 23:25:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电涨势提振情绪，亚洲股市上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市上涨，因台积电的前景激发了对该行业全球复苏的希望，在交易员寻找有关美联储下一步行动的线索之际提振了市场情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 22:21:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元主导地位正在引发整个市场的干预担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/dollar-dominance-is-triggering-intervention-fears-across-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美元的复苏引发了人们对官员们采取新措施保护本国货币的担忧，投资者再次重新制定干预策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/dollar-dominance-is-triggering-intervention-fears-across-markets</guid>
